text: Adile () is a Turkish feminine given name. Notable people with the name include: * Adile Ayda (1912–1992), first woman career diplomat of Turkey * Adile Naşit (1930–1987), Turkish actress * Adile Sultana (1825–1898), daughter of Sultan Mahmud II * Adile Zogu (1890–1966), sister of King Zog I == References == Category:Turkish feminine given names
title: Adile
